items.title: Colombian president says Venezuela "will implode" if U.S. runs country for years
items.description: President Gustavo Petro responded to President Trump's comment that he expected U.S. oversight of Venezuela to last "much longer" than a year.

items.title: U.S. sends delegation to Venezuela as Trump meets with oil executives
items.description: President Trump is meeting with oil industry executives at the White House as a U.S. delegation visits Venezuela.

items.title: Trump posted some U.S. jobs data the before its official release
items.description: The White House said it will review its protocols for releasing economic data after President Trump's "inadvertent public disclosure."

items.title: Watch Live: Trump meets with oil executives about Venezuela at White House
items.description: President Trump is meeting with big oil industry executives Friday afternoon as he pushes U.S. oil companies to invest in Venezuela.
